lyTime":"2017-06-12T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"仲唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1924354fbd7b292cdd744524841d207c461ed2","tid":280130,"uid":70886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:01:07.000Z","msg":"我屋企都好多德國小強 一到夏天好能恐怖<br />\n係荔枝角返工 有個婆婆賣小強藥 10蚊3包 聞陣味似奶粉<br />\n我分左幾廿份擺屋企d角落位<br />\n第二朝起身 地下d小強多到好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7065a2f74b798622623dc7ae20e643b466ee48e8","tid":280130,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"整隻四腳蛇落屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屋企啲四腳蛇唔多，不過我由細到大未試過喺屋企見過一隻曱甴"},{"pid":"69ea88781a648986238e602f3e338286cfb6833c","tid":280130,"uid":42945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"上淘寶買 拜滅士 小強藥，用左兩星期巳經無左9成。毒死左小強最好唔好執屍再等同伴食就可以滅族。<br />\n<br />\n以家好耐先見過一兩隻， 估計應該隔離屋過黎。"},{"pid":"0d8066a915cd2dea6aff4b053832f53b5d3edb27","tid":280130,"uid":53619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:14:17.000Z","msg":"引入美國蟑螂跟佢地互撕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5467a419a0af2f6a35ec0e80b8c62534e7529f79","tid":280130,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整隻四腳蛇落屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屋企啲四腳蛇唔多，不過我由細到大未試過喺屋企見過一隻曱甴</blockquote><br />\n神戰唔係可遇不可求嘅咩<br />\n我都未聽過可以主動養神獸係屋企"},{"pid":"7713461f5df718a2f5bf0581292e5e14f5a8e80a","tid":280130,"uid":65106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"睇過話月桂葉可以驅 磨粉效果更佳"},{"pid":"4dff630430b42d57db10d63207e20980d3977152","tid":280130,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"先執屋 清哂d雜物<br />\n再放強國既藥<br />\n好快死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c40847f5a0b6e0ddbbc34e080f6f53d5a3730d","tid":280130,"uid":11774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"我已經慣咗，初初會好驚，同佢對峙，唔敢郁，正所謂敵不動我不動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一動，佢仲走得快過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家？啲強變到唔驚人，我屋企嗰啲，行到勁近都唔會走，我都慣咗成日轉角遇到佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好幾代喺度"},{"pid":"ca7533dad0cfadc7636c988b836e1c2e871cf04d","tid":280130,"uid":2421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:35:04.000Z","msg":"同問 <br />\n有一日凌晨想飲水 一入廚房<br />\n見到有一隻勁大隻嘅 同啲bb玩得好開心<br />\n然後我殘忍咁殺撚死曬<br />\n唔想再晚晚一開燈就殺殺殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393ad980bd693e86f12411045853877cece7092a","tid":280130,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:40:47.000Z","msg":"宜家d強勁撚到連壁虎都殺得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好耐之前我屋企仲有甲由出沒<br />\n某一日我打開廚房門就見到有隻壁虎好可憐咁訓係地下<br />\n我篤下佢佢冇反應<br />\n可能同甲由大戰激烈過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以身殉國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我老母安葬左佢<br />\n<br />\n不過自此之後我就冇再見過屋企有甲由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能d甲由殺左人地老母比班細路殲滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(我屋企唔止一條壁虎 仲有d剛出細bb仔或者壁虎仔 好鐘意四圍爬)"},{"pid":"980b33db48965d125f792ae689e08b2263171f2c","tid":280130,"uid":32887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"有隻叫達豪滅蟑清  好有效<br />\n粉狀超甜餅味 但好撚毒<br />\n屋企無小朋友小動物先好買<br />\n我連用1星期 屋企已經無晒<br />\n而家一兩個月補1次 好撚無見過蟑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3740c3a2c05bc7945ec8a0d1d88d02b050e50b9","tid":280130,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:45:01.000Z","msg":"由屋外入黎既話我覺得用biokill去防都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企門外噴結介<br />\n有時係屋內近門位見屍"},{"pid":"5dc020c7a524dd94ab58ba6fb740fd79b4999253","tid":280130,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"03ed39d7396e2cec92fc3635c740d07033e77be3","tid":280130,"uid":54431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過話月桂葉可以驅 磨粉效果更佳</blockquote><br />\n月桂葉要係邊到捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d8f261a1771d9551ee4be5acf35b422cf5728b","tid":280130,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718c43308899380116f996265b5732c14052b4da","tid":280130,"uid":66032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我已經慣咗，初初會好驚，同佢對峙，唔敢郁，正所謂敵不動我不動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一動，佢仲走得快過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家？啲強變到唔驚人，我屋企嗰啲，行到勁近都唔會走，我都慣咗成日轉角遇到佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好幾代喺度</blockquote><br />\n一野拍死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea5926454eac91541c5ab1c58e51a610b838082","tid":280130,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"我癲到係房食野 但都無小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f23f3f2d0e1377f312025ef9b1bdca46ec1865","tid":280130,"uid":16511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有隻叫達豪滅蟑清  好有效<br />\n粉狀超甜餅味 但好撚毒<br />\n屋企無小朋友小動物先好買<br />\n我連用1星期 屋企已經無晒<br />\n而家一兩個月補1次 好撚無見過蟑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlm"},{"pid":"c2bb8aac9835990fd0b2bbe3c6334bb536e63705","tid":280130,"uid":74715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家d強勁撚到連壁虎都殺得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好耐之前我屋企仲有甲由出沒<br />\n某一日我打開廚房門就見到有隻壁虎好可憐咁訓係地下<br />\n我篤下佢佢冇反應<br />\n可能同甲由大戰激烈過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以身殉國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我老母安葬左佢<br />\n<br />\n不過自此之後我就冇再見過屋企有甲由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能d甲由殺左人地老母比班細路殲滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(我屋企唔止一條壁虎 仲有d剛出細bb仔或者壁虎仔 好鐘意四圍爬)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企都有好多<br />\n但佢地唔會同啲曱甴大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a7dcdbb1193d2510421b9782fdef371e663ff1","tid":280130,"uid":15479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"屌 每年夏天都會有甲由係我張床度<br />\n上個月有隻甲由仲要趁我訓著 <br />\n爬係我個頭度行黎行去 <br />\n<br />\n最煩係屋企有小動物 唔可以用毒性太強既藥<br />\n點解甲由殺極都極唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201e751dad601e9e7c877a13ee85fe785143250a","tid":280130,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"諗住揾日用殺蟲煙霧<br />\n跟住將廚房d野洗一次<br />\n順便睇有乜可以掉<br />\n應該搞成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c636c6234b787ec4360827f381c575c11eb71411","tid":280130,"uid":20951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>引入美國蟑螂跟佢地互撕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1021662255196181dd0b4d75f27696edf98fe0","tid":280130,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfb5157fc0cda0ee526cf937c2d7e0a07a274a8f","tid":280130,"uid":118023,"like":0,"dislik