6f9","tid":280130,"uid":96457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"晚晚開燈都要殺十幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但大家無把握一炮清唔好去馬 試過佢地由廁所搬去廳再搬左入廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184c533afc362363af1d94d07a63aae6276615ce","tid":280130,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晚晚開燈都要殺十幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但大家無把握一炮清唔好去馬 試過佢地由廁所搬去廳再搬左入廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都驚呢樣野, 走出廳就大獲"},{"pid":"42dba1bb1cb10265b975132ef375cea35ffc6ebe","tid":280130,"uid":89111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n依加用殺蟲水都殺唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n殺極仲有 一到夏天就量産<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a055394c5355ea2a15530c9e7a56c0e6ce2d00","tid":280130,"uid":83809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"有小動物係咪只可用屋黎捉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12b0f8a014620ec687114a78112c9b738170132","tid":280130,"uid":83809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/155/d155252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F155%2Fd155252.jpg&h=7f1f1dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://clps10160813.weebly.com/uploads/1/3/5/2/13527255/1052077_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclps10160813.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F3%2F5%2F2%2F13527255%2F1052077_orig.jpg&h=4fab79bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頂你食緊野睇到打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83b31f54baf9618248f15c6ba4e15721de86ae3","tid":280130,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去超市買果d黑色細細盒既，可以俾佢捐個頭入去食毒藥，帶返去佢屋企然後殺埋全家，一殺十，十殺百，好快ko晒<br />\n<br />\n利申：以前試過屋企多到夜晚天花會好多甲由係度飛，之後就冇晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有買 完全冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我聽人做過藥廠公司話其實隻藥係有用<br />\n但香港天氣太潮濕<br />\n開左幾日潮左變無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb2b7d7361064703dd32ca78bf7843a3eeef94c","tid":280130,"uid":107605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/155/d155252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F155%2Fd155252.jpg&h=7f1f1dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://clps10160813.weebly.com/uploads/1/3/5/2/13527255/1052077_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclps10160813.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F3%2F5%2F2%2F13527255%2F1052077_orig.jpg&h=4fab79bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n大隻係樣衰啲, 但易搞<br />\n細隻果啲好難搞</blockquote><br />\n你老母比曱甴屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cfbaa749648270ca2ec5235c82ace0eff9a5bf","tid":280130,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:15:02.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n屋企有小動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前排用啲冇咁毒嘅藥<br />\n結果學巴打話齋走曬出廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋晚仲入埋房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baaf7d7c0aac0f71638b24e3ca852bb6c4f4e55","tid":280130,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:19:11.000Z","msg":"其實啲細曱甴係邊度黎,"},{"pid":"3da2fe0100ca72e7c4360d03bba5bc84e2633086","tid":280130,"uid":11222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"一點絕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8feb5fc4853a0ffdb9e83dd7d3094a8f47cd4b40","tid":280130,"uid":13335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"有次有隻大強唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來走左入我房<br />\n我又唔知<br />\n之後有晚我熄晒燈係到煲劇<br />\n忽然隻大強爬左落個mon到<br />\n嚇撚到我high high<br />\n因為我睇手機會放好近面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自從果次我就一獲鏟起晒佢地<br />\n又放曱甴屋又落藥又養簷蛇<br />\n表示洗衣機底有一家大細<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重要都係保持家居清潔<br />\n依家好耐冇見過"},{"pid":"ef24a427df5c18541ff8db4fbfccdfaf15bcdca9","tid":280130,"uid":35066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"班仆街一夏天就出番哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經殺到懶 日日瘋狂扑野 點殺得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37091d44093a878c1cf9597b661e0176b07501c3","tid":280130,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"係咪有錢人屋企先無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac85f7bd06e9e0feecd379e51516b2ce1a6d3cb","tid":280130,"uid":12537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有錢人屋企先無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗要好有錢先冇<br />\n有親戚住九龍塘果堆食個飯都見到飛甲同成堆b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能因為住2、3樓，賓妹又唔識滅蟲"},{"pid":"893a1a4c41817b0b6a32b83599315fad384800e4","tid":280130,"uid":9741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"淘寶淘左一點絕 <br />\n小左9成 不過幾貴 但值"},{"pid":"eab9cc0fb0399d74fca2c3bddca3c3b3d7630494","tid":280130,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"淘寶甲由藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931d5baec1d05b3b9e8836f70adc3ba747d9b87a","tid":280130,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"窮撚屋企表示無曱甴<br />\n最緊要係少雜物同保持乾淨"},{"pid":"703958cf5444634a6e02899b19cecffd1852274e","tid":280130,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"試過用炸彈 一出煙就成蟑螂屍體"},{"pid":"e928ac04664be3734552774c2a5aa72c660c4175","tid":280130,"uid":35066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"其實班仆街係黎自邊度? 我都係呢幾年先出現<br />\n住廿幾樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就黎要搞到屋企長期好似北海道咁先可以滅種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6861e7719849df1fbc950befb8b57e20764278d","tid":280130,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮撚屋企表示無曱甴<br />\n最緊要係少雜物同保持乾淨</blockquote><br />\n自問好乾淨，舊屋住廿幾年見過1,2隻出面走入黎<br />\n一搬新屋多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2917e982f3371af23cd0022615945593aace903d","tid":280130,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮撚屋企表示無曱甴<br />\n最緊要係少雜物同保持乾淨</blockquote><br />\n有時唔係自己屋企搞到咁 而係樓上樓下成棟樓搞到你屋企有"},{"pid":"c1592a4a998ae3d70eaf73fd1ee9aecf770e1ca0","tid":280130,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockqu